{
  "texts": [
    "3D-PCPR technology has witnessed widespread application and rapid development.",
    "Single frame-based 3D-PCPR methods, exemplified by high-accuracy algorithms like Min-kLoc3Dv2 (Komorowski 2022) and others, have achieved remarkable progress.",
    "However, despite these advancements, numerous challenges and open issues remain to be addressed in this field.",
    "Based on our comprehensive analysis of over 180 research works, we now delve into the future research trends of 3D-PCPR.",
    "By providing a concise overview, we aim to inspire and guide future researchers in their exploration of this domain."
  ]
}